605
00:29:40.068 --> 00:29:42.276
then it's observation.
with the surgery the day after.

606
00:29:46.901 --> 00:29:49.943
Do you know that Mohanlal and
Dulquer Salmaan have houses in Chennai?

607
00:29:50.401 --> 00:29:51.401
