♪ Our Lord Karuppu Saamy.
Come. and scorch our doubts completely ♪

1703
01:35:02.193 --> 01:35:05.026
♪ Our Lord Karuppu Saamy.
Our Lord Karuppu Saamy ♪

1704
01:35:05.360 --> 01:35:08.568
♪ Come. soothe my heart.
Come. burn all doubt apart ♪

1705
