at having triumphed.

2494
02:25:29.276 --> 02:25:31.110
A newfound hope for the future.

2495
02:25:31.651 --> 02:25:34.544
The only place that can
grant all these emotions equally.

2496
02:25:34.568 --> 02:25:38.544
