2527
02:27:54.985 --> 02:27:58.235
Dr. Usilampatti Karuppaiah Gandhi!

2528
02:28:12.735 --> 02:28:14.193
Honourable Speaker!

2529
02:28:14.318 --> 02:28:16.776
Wondering how I'd save
Tamil Nadu all by myself.

2530
02:28:16.818 --> 02:28:18.193
