concern for the people...

2532
02:28:21.651 --> 02:28:23.360
I'm inspired to save Tamil Nadu!

2533
02:28:26.401 --> 02:28:28.276
From 1958 till date.

2534
02:28:28.526 --> 02:28:30.294
